{"tid":2272363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國外交部：盼美國新一屆政府與中方秉持不衝突不對抗","createTime":"2020-11-05T04:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T04:41:20.000Z","uid":156254,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"111f3bbb6012e6bf2c6bb2fa562ccba03c75bf36","tid":2272363,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"中國外交部：盼美國新一屆政府與中方秉持不衝突不對抗<br />\n2020-11-05 HKT 11:57<br />\n 分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n<br />\n仇志榮在北京報道<br />\n在北京，外交部副部長樂玉成說，很關注美國大選，希望大選能夠平穩、順利舉行。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成期望，美國新一屆政府與中方相向而行，秉持不衝突、不對抗、相互尊重、聚焦合作、管控分歧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558495-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558495-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4GINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=88241b60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558495-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=426eb876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558495-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818bfd2eea0cf75239d7fc13c844223d55313b6a","tid":2272363,"uid":67280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"咁快爆大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2be24b9c73b8b64ccc7b25f77965fab5d1abef","tid":2272363,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0phcRj8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0phcRj8.png&h=fced7bbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d6d6